"results for it! Nagios will ignore all check results for services that had "
"not been configured before it was last (re)started."
msgstr ""

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><tip><para>
#: TheBasics/passivechecks.xml:189
msgid ""
"An example shell script of how to submit passive service check results to "
"Nagios can be found in the documentation on <link linkend=\"advancedtopics-"
"volatileservices\">volatile services</link>."
msgstr ""

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><title>
#: TheBasics/passivechecks.xml:195
msgid "Submitting Passive Host Check Results"
